The bamphomet simply chuckled at Chaostaur as he threatened him. A moment 
alter the bot slowly hovered into the air in front of Chaostaur as its body 
began to crackle with power.

Bamphomet: "Now listen to me. You will do what I say, when I say, and not a 
second sooner or later. What ever you did in the past no longer matters. You 
belong to me... serve me well and you shall be rewarded. Fail me... and you 
will be snuffed out as easily as a candle."

--part1_f4.16124e46.298cc63a_boundary
